# Keep the Docker build context lean for Dockerfile.serve and Dockerfile.hostile.
# Everything the Go builds need (sources, go.mod/sum, embedded *.bd assets) stays;
# only heavy generated/VCS trees are excluded. frontend/dist is regenerated as a
# stub inside Dockerfile.hostile, so excluding the (usually symlinked) node_modules
# and any stale dist is safe.
.git
frontend/node_modules
frontend/dist
build/bin
doc/build
